			<notes/>
			<notesNormalized/>
			<notesHtml/>
			<text>Learning objectives
Describe the basic epidemiology of mental health conditions in the population

Describe the risk factors for significant psychological distress and potential of different life events to provoke stress and psychological disorder 

Plus:

Discuss effective public health interventions, government targets and guidance in relation to mental illness and substance misuse</text>
		</slide>
		<slide index="2" title="Key Facts" titleNormalized="key facts" src="slide3.swf" size="1884" advanceOnTime="0" framesCount="1" hasEmbeddedFlashClip="0" hidden="0" level="0" advanceOnClick="1" thumbnailAssetId="imgAsset2">
